questions.quote: Look, I know what you're going through. When I turned 50 I got the Porsche. You... you got your own little speedster.
Yeah...I mean I want this so much! I mean, I wanna get one, I want my friend Charlie to get one...Except I don't care about Charlie.
That's right. That is right, you go over there and tell her you don't want her to live with you. Do not take no for an answer!
I'll be fine, alright? Really, everyone. I hope she'll be very happy.
Well, I'm telling everyone about you! That's the only way to explain the underwear and the video camera that doesn't make me look like a pig!
Look, when I've been drinking, sometimes I tend to get overly friendly, and I'm sorry.
Ok, now that your coat is safely in the bedr-, oh, ok we can come back out in the living room.
No! I talked to Joey on the set, he hasn't heard from him. I-I-I talked to Chandler's parents again!
Well so, how come you blew me off? Y'know? How come you were with him?
You know when guys hang out they don't just drink some beer and hammer up drywall?
